<h1>This email is a confirmation for your FlightFinder booking!</h1>
<p>Hello <%= @passenger.name.capitalize %>,</p>
<p>
  Your flight is on <%= @flight.departure_time.strftime("%m-%d-%Y, at %H:%M")%> GMT. Your flight will depart from <%= @flight.departure_airport.code %> airport and arrive at <%= @flight.arrival_airport.code %> airport.
</p>
<p>To see more details about your flight, including seating information, please <a href="<%= @url %>">click here!</a></p>

<p>Thank you for signing up with FlightFinder!</p>